DTV%20in%20Hanle%2C%20Ajay%20Talwar%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BIt%20has%20been%20more%20than%2025%20years%20since%20I%20began%20photographing%20the%20night%20skies%20but%20I%20still%20remember%20the%20first%20time%20I%20did%20it.%20Although%20I%20have%20lost%20the%20slide%2C%20I%20still%20remember%20it%20vividly.%20I%20had%20gone%20to%20a%20place%20called%20Neb%20Sarai%20on%20the%20outskirts%20of%20Delhi%20in%201987%20and%20exposed%20an%20entire%20film%20for%20a%20night.%20The%20slide%20film%20had%2036%20frames%2C%20but%20just%20a%20couple%20had%20stars%20visible%20in%20them.%20An%20employee%20at%20the%20shop%20where%20I%20got%20the%20film%20developed%20had%20almost%20thrown%20the%20film%20in%20the%20bin%2C%20because%20he%20did%20not%20find%20it%20exposed%20at%20all.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20passion%20shining%20through%2C%20Ajay%20said%20that%20there%20was%20one%20frame%20which%20was%20loaded%20with%20stars%20and%20the%20Omega%20Centauri%20cluster%20was%20clearly%20visible.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20was%20really%20happy.%20That%20was%20my%20impetus%2C%20my%20drive%20to%20continue%20astrophotography%20till%20now.%20As%20the%20results%20got%20better%2C%20I%20wanted%20to%20do%20more%20and%20more.%20I%20would%20describe%20my%20work%20as%20the%20TWAN%20style.%20A%20couple%20of%20years%20ago%2C%20I%20was%20invited%20to%20become%20a%20member%20of%20'The%20World%20At%20Night'%20(TWAN)%20from%20India.%20TWAN%20members%20specialise%20in%20what%20is%20called%20Earth%20and%20Sky%20photography%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Ajay.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-10%2Fn5dboig8_astrophotography_625x300_02_October_24.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20a%20style%20where%20you%20photograph%20celestial%20bodies%20along%20with%20famous%20monuments%2C%20natural%20wonders%20and%20popular%20places.%20There%20are%20about%2030%20TWAN%20photographers%20spread%20out%20all%20over%20the%20world%20and%20they%20shoot%20stunning%20night%20landscapes.%20This%20is%20a%20genre%20of%20astrophotography%20which%20lay%20people%20relate%20to%20and%20understand%20at%20a%20glance%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-10%2Fqsd0gap_astrophotography_625x300_02_October_24.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAjay%20said%20patience%20is%20required%20in%20abundance%20for%20astrophotography%20and%20in%20the%20days%20when%20film%20was%20used%2C%20it%20would%20take%20several%20minutes%20just%20to%20expose%20one%20frame.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20one%20night%2C%20the%20entire%20film%20of%2036%20frames%20would%20not%20even%20be%20complete%2C%20so%20you%20were%20forced%20to%20go%20out%20again%20a%20week%20or%20month%20later.%20Finally%2C%20the%20film%20would%20be%20complete%20and%20then%20you%20would%20go%20and%20get%20it%20developed.%20So%20you%20would%20get%20to%20see%20the%20fruits%20only%20about%20a%20month%20later%20and%20still%20run%20the%20risk%20of%20making%20a%20mistake%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-10%2Frngmmc9o_astrophotography_625x300_02_October_24.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDigital%20cameras%20changed%20this%20drastically.%20You%20can%20preview%20your%20images%20instantly%2C%20make%20corrections%20immediately%20and%20come%20back%20home%20with%20at%20least%20a%20few%20good%20shots.%20Even%20now%2C%20with%20advanced%20digital%20cameras%2C%20plenty%20of%20patience%20is%20required%20as%20you%20are%20photographing%20all%20night%20in%20some%20cases%2C%26quot%3B%20Ajay%20pointed%20out.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1727917980000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-10%2Fe27fsfa_astrophotography_625x300_02_October_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fajay-and-neelam-talwar-hanle-astrophotography-at-indias-only-dark-sky-reserve-stargazing-couple-is-star-attraction-6701136%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Patience%20is%20the%20key%2C%20and%20it%20can%20pay%20handsomely%20-%20this%20is%20the%20message%20that%20Ajay%20and%20Neelam%20Talwar%2C%20a%20unique%20stargazing%20couple%20who%20have%20spent%20more%20than%2025%20years%20photographing%20celestial%20bodies%2C%20have%20for%20people%20wanting%20to%20take%20up%20astrophotography.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fajay-and-neelam-talwar-hanle-astrophotography-at-indias-only-dark-sky-reserve-stargazing-couple-is-star-attraction-6701136%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'It%E2%80%99s%20Kam-a-la%20Harris'%3A%20CNN%20anchor%20gets%20into%20heated%20argument%20with%20Trump%20aide%20after%20repeated%20mispronunciation%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1727917916000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-113889958%2Cimgsize-702334.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fits-kam-a-la-harris-cnn-anchor-gets-into-heated-exchange-with-trump-aide-after-repeated-mispronunciation-us-elections-corey-lewandowski-jim-acosta%2Farticleshow%2F113889925.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F113889925.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3ECNN%20anchor%20Jim%20Acosta%20cut%20short%20an%20interview%20with%20Corey%20Lewan