ot%3B%20Judge%20Diwakar%20warned.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlim%2C%20a%20native%20of%20Jadaunpur%20village%20of%20the%20Devarnia%20area%2C%20had%20deceived%20the%20woman%20by%20posing%20as%20'Anand'.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20also%20ordered%20that%20copies%20of%20the%20ruling%20be%20sent%20to%20the%20Chief%20Secretary%20and%20the%20Director%20General%20of%20Police.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20said%20that%20conversions%20are%20being%20conducted%20through%20psychological%20pressure%20and%20inducements%20such%20as%20marriage%20and%20jobs%2C%20and%20also%20expressed%20concerns%20about%20potential%20foreign%20funding.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20the%20issue%20is%20not%20addressed%20in%20time%2C%20it%20could%20lead%20to%20severe%20consequences%2C%20it%20observed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20pointed%20out%20that%20the%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20government%20enacted%20the%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20Prohibition%20of%20Unlawful%20Religious%20Conversion%20Act%2C%202021%2C%20specifically%20to%20combat%20illegal%20conversions%20through%20%26quot%3BLove%20Jihad.%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BThe%20Constitution%20grants%20every%20individual%20the%20fundamental%20right%20to%20practice%20and%20propagate%20their%20religion%2C%20and%20this%20personal%20freedom%20cannot%20be%20compromised%20through%20illegal%20conversions%20facilitated%20by%20'Love%20Jihad'%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20noted.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1727894700000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2Fcourt-generic_625x300_1527245477936.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flove-jihad-big-threat-to-nations-unity-says-up-court-sentences-man-6699686%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20objective%20of%20%26quot%3Blove%20jihad%26quot%3B%20is%20to%20establish%20dominance%20by%20certain%20anti-social%20elements%20of