hut%20down%20the%20runway%2C%20%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.scmp.com%2Fnews%2Fasia%2Feast-asia%2Farticle%2F3280799%2Fjapan-shuts-regional-airport-after-likely-ww2-era-bomb-explodes-near-runway%5C%22%3ESouth%20China%20Morning%20Post%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported.%C2%A0According%20to%20Japan's%20Transport%20Ministry%2C%20a%20bomb%20disposal%20team%20confirmed%20the%20explosion%20was%20caused%20by%20an%20American%20bomb%20buried%20beneath%20the%20surface%2C%20dating%20back%20to%20a%20wartime%20air%20raid.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFortunately%2C%20no%20injuries%20were%20reported.%20The%20runway%20shutdown%20has%20led%20to%20the%20grounding%20of%2087%20flights%20but%20there%20is%20no%20danger%20of%20any%20further%20explosions.%20Repairs%20to%20fill%20the%20crater%20are%20expected%20to%20be%20completed%20by%20Thursday%20morning%2C%20said%20Japan's%20top%20government%20spokesperson%2C%20Yoshimasa%20Hayashi.%20The%20officials%20are%20also%20determining%20what%20caused%20its%20sudden%20detonation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20disruption%20at%20Miyazaki%20Airport%20impacted%20flights%20operated%20by%20major%20carriers%20Japan%20Airlines%20(JAL)%20and%20All%20Nippon%20Airways%20(ANA)%2C%20as%20well%20as%20other%20airlines.%20These%20affected%20flights%20typically%20connect%20Miyazaki%20with%20key%20Japanese%20cities%2C%20including%20Tokyo%2C%20Osaka%2C%20and%20Fukuoka%2C%20according%20to%20the%20airport's%20website.%20The%20airlines%20affected%20are%20working%20to%20resume%20normal%20operations%20as%20soon%20as%20possible%2C%20following%20the%20completion%20of%20repairs%20to%20the%20damaged%20taxiway.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20unexploded%20bombs%20remain%20a%20persistent%20threat.%20Despite%20being%20over%2079%20years%20since%20the%20war's%20end%2C%20multiple%20unexploded%20bombs%20have%20previously%20been%20found%20at%20Miyazaki%20airport%2C%20as%20per%20the%20transport%20ministry.%C2%A0%20In%202023%20alone%2C%20the%20Self-Defense%20Forces%20disposed%20of%202%2C348%20bombs%20weighing%2037.5%20tonnes.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOriginally%20a%20Japanese%20naval%20base%20during%20World%20War%20II%2C%20the%20Miyazaki%20airport%20has%20since%20transitioned%20to%20civilian%20use.%C2%A0Located%20in%20Miyazaki%20Prefecture%2C%20it%20is%20a%20regional%20airport%20serving%20domestic%20and%20international%20flights.%20It%20features%20one%202%2C500-meter%20runway%20and%20a%20single%20terminal%20handling%20both%20domestic%20and%20international%20operations.%20Major%20airlines%20such%20as%20Japan%20Airlines%2C%20All%20Nippon%20Airways%2C%20and%20Solaseed%20Air%20operate%20from%20Miyazaki%2C%20connecting%20passengers%20to%20key%20destinations%20like%20Tokyo%2C%20Osaka%2C%20and%20Fukuoka%2C%20and%20international%20routes%20to%20Taiwan%20and%20South%20Korea.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1727881980000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-10%2F8lpd3qd8_world-war-ii-bomb_625x300_02_October_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fjapan-airport-shut-after-world-war-ii-bomb-explodes-near-runway-87-flights-cancelled-6701776%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22According%20to%20Japan's%20Transport%20Ministry%2C%20a%20bomb%20disposal%20team%20confirmed%20the%20explosion%20was%20caused%20by%20an%20American%20bomb%20buried%20beneath%20the%20surface%2C%20dating%20back%20to%20a%20wartime%20air%20raid.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fjapan-airport-shut-after-world-war-ii-bomb-explodes-near-runway-87-flights-cancelled-6701776%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Israel%20has%20upper%20hand%20in%20tit-for-tat%20air%20war%20-%20especially%20with%20US%20support%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1727881440000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F24%2F10%2F1920x1080%2Fskynews-israel-air-defence-systems_6704319.jpg%3F20241002163733%2