0I%20had%20swam%20out%20into%20the%20sea%20to%20rescue%20someone.%20We%20didn%E2%80%99t%20even%20have%20proper%20equipment%20like%20a%20surfboard%2C%20walkie-talkie%2C%20lifeguard%20jeep%2C%20or%20jet-ski%2C%E2%80%9D%20recalls%20Shashikant.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20lack%20of%20coordination%2C%20equipment%2C%20and%20professionalism%20was%20reflected%20in%20the%20lack%20of%20beach%20safety%20and%20the%20number%20of%20drowning%20deaths%20Goa%20saw.%20Matters%20came%20to%20a%20head%20in%202007%20when%20the%20state%20unfortunately%20saw%20200%20people%20drown%20off%20the%20coastline%2C%20according%20to%20news%20reports.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20Rajiv%20Somani%2C%20founder%20and%20chairperson%20of%20Drishti%20Marine%2C%20notes%2C%20%E2%80%9CFollowing%20the%20events%20of%202007%2C%20the%20State%20Government%20was%20prompted%20to%20take%20immediate%20measures%20and%20put%20together%20an%20efficient%20system%20to%20safeguard%20lives%20along%20beaches.%20One%20of%20the%20measures%20adopted%20by%20the%20State%20Government%20was%20to%20appoint%20a%20professional%20agency%20for%20enhancing%20beach%20safety.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20500px)%20100vw%2C%20500px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FImage-2-1727448639-500x556.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Drishti%20'Lifesavers'%20(lifeguards)%20saving%20lives%20in%20Goa.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FImage-2-1727448639-500x556.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FImage-2-1727448639-270x300.jpg%20270w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FImage-2-1727448639-768x855.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FImage-2-1727448639.jpg%201080w%2C%20https%