ic%20pollution%2C%E2%80%9D%20Utsow%20informs%20me%20as%20we%20sit%20in%20one%20of%20his%20mud%20houses%2C%20sipping%20fresh%20Darjeeling%20tea.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20compound%20has%20since%20transformed%20into%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F353885%2Fbrigadiers-cottage-homestay-mussoorie-uttarakhand-aseem-neetu-varma-sistainable-travel%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ean%20eco-resort%20with%20its%20own%20waste%20segregation%20and%20composting%20facilities%3C%2Fa%3E.%20It%20features%20a%20few%20cottages%20built%20from%20mud%20and%20bamboo%2C%20where%20guests%20often%20visit%20to%20contribute%20to%20the%20various%20initiatives%20Tieedi%20has%20undertaken.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUtsow%2C%20who%20spent%20his%20formative%20years%20in%20Kurseong%20%E2%80%94%20a%20tiny%20municipality%20about%2040%20km%20away%20from%20Darjeeling%20%E2%80%94%20says%20that%20the%20transformation%20he%20witnessed%20over%20the%20years%20pushed%20him%20further%20to%20explore%20ways%20in%20which%20sustainability%20and%20development%20could%20coexist.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CEarlier%2C%20I%20remember%20about%20five%20concrete%20shops%20when%20I%20first%20visited%20the%20compound%20in%20Gorabari.%20There%20were%20over%20fifty%20now%20along%20that%20one-kilometre%20stretch%20of%20road%2C%E2%80%9D%20Utsow%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20992px)%20100vw%2C%20992px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-09-27-at-18.58.56_11zon-1727443840.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22992%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20dog%20stays%20guard%20on%20a%20path%20leading%20up%20to%20one%20of%20the%20eco-huts%20in%20Tieedi%2C%20a%20large%20part%20of%20which%20was%20once%20a%20dump%20yard.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-09-27-at-