l%20media%20has%20turned%20the%20world%20into%20a%20global%20village%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20where%20everything%20and%20everyone%2C%20no%20matter%20how%20far%2C%20feels%20close.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20a%20burning%20desire%20to%20pursue%20her%20passion%20and%20share%20her%20art%20with%20the%20world%2C%20Varsha%20uploaded%20her%20first%20video.%20What%20began%20as%20short%20dance%20and%20comedy%20clips%20soon%20evolved%20into%20something%20bigger.%20But%20every%20coin%20has%20two%20sides.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInitially%2C%20she%20faced%20harsh%20mockery%20and%20trolls%20hiding%20behind%20their%20screens%2C%20trying%20to%20pull%20her%20down.%20Varsha%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20one%20to%20give%20up%20easily.%20She%20flipped%20the%20coin%20%E2%80%94%20and%20her%20story.%20Her%20content%20began%20to%20gain%20traction%2C%20and%20soon%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F255612%2Fsocial-media-influencer-instagram-senior-citizens-mr-mrs-verma-yashpal-singh-shanta-jonita-haryana-trends-online-collaboration-romance-old-age-boredom-lockdown-inspirational-vid01%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eher%20videos%20began%20going%20viral%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CPeople%20laughed%20at%20me%20at%20first%2C%E2%80%9D%20Varsha%20shared.%20%E2%80%9CBut%20then%20something%20incredible%20happened.%20My%20videos%20started%20to%20take%20off%2C%20and%20suddenly%2C%20people%20were%20following%20my%20journey.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20talent%20and%20charm%20earned%20her%20a%20spot%20on%20the%20popular%20dance%20reality%20show%20%3Cem%3EDance%20Deewane%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%20where%20she%20wowed%20both%20the%20judges%20and%20the%20audience.%20One%20of%20the%20judges%20told%20her%2C%20%E2%80%9CYou%E2%80%99re%20a%20real%20hero.%20People%20need%20to%20learn%20from%20you.%20You%20didn%E2%80%99t%20let%20life%20drown%20you%20%E2%80%94%20you%20fought%20back.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20an%20emotional%20moment%20