t-attack-detect-cardiac-symptoms-ecg-device-sanketlife-rahul-neha-rastogi-noida%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EWorld%20Heart%20Day%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20we%20aim%20to%20shift%20the%20narrative%20to%20the%20often-ignored%20subject%20of%20women%E2%80%99s%20heart%20health.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELife%20was%20routine%20for%2040-year-old%20Neha%20until%20an%20incident%20shook%20her%20world.%20The%20Haridwar%20resident%20started%20experiencing%20sudden%20dizziness%20and%20fainting%20episodes%2C%20blacking%20out%20for%20a%20few%20seconds%20before%20regaining%20consciousness.%20This%20happened%20four%20to%20five%20times%20over%20two%20days.%20She%20visited%20a%20local%20doctor%20who%20advised%20her%20to%20immediately%20seek%20treatment%20from%20a%20specialist%20in%20Dehradun.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20conducting%20ECGs%20and%20other%20basic%20tests%2C%20the%20doctor%20in%20Dehradun%20realised%20that%20these%20were%20symptoms%20of%20sudden%20cardiac%20arrests%20and%20referred%20her%20to%20the%20Fortis%20Escorts%20Heart%20Institute%20in%20New%20Delhi%2C%20where%20she%20proceeded%20for%20treatment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Aparna%20Jaswal%2C%20Director%20of%20Cardiology%2C%20Department%20of%20Cardiac%20Pacing%20and%20Electrophysiology%20at%20Fortis%2C%20identified%20Neha%E2%80%99s%20symptoms%20as%20a%20heart%20ailment%2C%20explaining%20that%20her%20sudden%20fainting%20episodes%20were%20the%20result%20of%20cardiac%20arrest.%20They%20were%20able%20to%20identify%20the%20ailment%20through%20continuous%20heart%20monitoring.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENeha%E2%80%99s%20case%20is%20not%20the%20only%20one.%20The%20prevalence%20of%20coronary%20artery%20diseases%20in%20women%20range%20from%20three%20to%2013%20percent%2C%20according%20to%20a%20report%20in%20the%20%3Cem%3EJournal%20of%20the%20American%20College%20of%20Cardiology%3C%2Fem%3E.%20The%20report%20also%20states%20that%20the%20disease%20has%20increased%20by%20over%20300%20percent%20in%20the%20past%2020%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20Global%20Burden%20of%20Disease%20Study%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F341755%2Fcongenital-heart-disease-in-babies-treatment-surgery-provided-by-hans-foundation%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eheart%20disease%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20a%20leading%20cause%20of%20fatality%20among%20Indian%20women%2C%20accounting%20for%20over%2017%20percent%20of%20deaths.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20alarming%20statistic%20underscores%20the%20importance%20of%20recognising%20the%20unique%20ways%20heart%20diseases%20manifest%20in%20women%2C%20as%20well%20as%20the%20critical%20need%20for%20awareness%20and%20proactive%20health%20management.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHeart%20disease%20is%20the%20biggest%20killer%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHeart%20disease%20refers%20to%20a%20range%20of%20conditions%20like%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F336492%2Fgoan-artist-xavier-fernandes-makes-christmas-cribs-from-driftwood%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecoronary%20artery%20disease%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20congenital%20heart%20disease%2C%20arrhythmia%20(irregular%20heartbeats)%2C%20cardiac%20arrest%2C%20and%20more.%20It%20is%20one%20of%20the%20leading%20causes%20of%20death%20worldwide.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20more%20often%20than%20not%2C%20heart%20diseases%20are%20preventable%20and%20can%20be%20successfully%20treated%20if%20diagnosed%20early.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20traditional%20belief%20is%20that%20heart%20diseases%20generally%20affect%20women%2010%20years%20later%20than%20men%2C%20this%20is%20no%20longer%20the%20case.%20Just%20like%20younger%20men%20are%20getting%20heart%20attacks%2C%20so%20are%20women%2C%20but%20they%20are%20often%20unaware%20of%20the%20signs%20and%20symptoms.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201280px)%20100vw%2C%201280px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fheart-care-1040227_1280-1727414916.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fheart-care-1040227_1280-1727414916.jpg%201280w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fheart-care-1040227_1280-1727414916-300x212.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fheart-care-1040227_1280-1727414916-500x354.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fheart-care-1040227_1280-1727414916-768x543.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fheart-care-1040227_1280-1727414916-150x106.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-367768%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22905%5C%22%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20doctors%2C%20the%20first%20vital%20step%20is%20to%20address%20a%20common%20misconception%20that%20cardiovascular%20diseases%2C%20including%20heart%20attacks%2C%20affect%20men%20more%20than%20women.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CA%20critical%20difference%20is%20that%20women%20often%20experience%20%E2%80%98silent%E2%80%99%20heart%20diseases%2C%20where%20symptoms%20may%20not%20be%20as%20pronounced%20or%20may%20be%20misattributed%20to%20other%20conditions.%20This%20often%20leads%20to%20delays%20in%20diagnosis%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Dr%20Ravinder%20Singh%20Rao%2C%20interventional%20structural%20cardiologist%2C%20chairman%20at%20RHL%20Center%2C%20Jaipur%2C%20and%20consultant%20at%20Lilavati%20Hospital%20and%20Research%20Centre%2C%20Mumbai.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETherefore%2C%20it%20is%20imperative%20for%20women%20to%20be%20aware%20of%20the%20symptoms%20and%20to%20seek%20immediate%20hospital%20care%20whenever%20they%20experience%20them.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ESymptoms%20of%20a%20heart%20attack%3A%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20usual%20symptoms%20common%20across%20genders%20include%20chest%20pain%2C%20pressure%20or%20discomfort%20that%20lasts%20more%20than%20a%20few%20minutes%20or%20recurs%2C%20Dr%20Rao%20informs.%20However%2C%20he%20adds%20that%20chest%20pain%20experienced%20by%20women%20may%20differ%20slightly%20from%20that%20experienced%20by%20men%2C%20often%20described%20more%20as%20pressure%20or%20tightness.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COther%20symptoms%20seen%20in%20women%20include%20neck%2C%20jaw%20and%20shoulder%20pain%2C%20shortness%20of%20breath%2C%20pain%20in%20one%20or%20both%20arms%2C%20nausea%20or%20vomiting%2C%20sweating%2C%20or%20dizziness.%20Women%20should%20be%20particularly%20cautious%20about%20atypical%20symptoms%2C%20as%20they%20may%20not%20be%20recognised%20as%20signs%20of%20a%20heart%20attack%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Jaswal%20adds%20that%20dizziness%2C%20blurring%20or%20fainting%2C%20radiating%20pain%20to%20the%20shoulders%20and%20jaw%2C%20extreme%20fatigue%20or%20breathlessness%2C%20and%20palpitations%20are%20also%20symptoms%20seen%20in%20women.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FCopy-of-Infographic-website-3-1727414804.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FCopy-of-Infographic-website-3-1727414804.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FCopy-of-Infographic-website-3-1727414804-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FCopy-of-Infographic-website-3-1727414804-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FCopy-of-Infographic-website-3-1727414804-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FCopy-of-Infographic-website-3-1727414804-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-367765%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3E(Symptoms%20from%20the%20World%20Heart%20Federation)%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20informs%20that%20earlier%2C%20hormones%20were%20believed%20to%20provide%20protection%20against%20heart%20diseases%20till%20menopause%2C%20when%20the%20levels%20dropped.%20However%2C%20that%20is%20not%20the%20case%20today%2C%20as%20younger%20women%2C%20too%2C%20experience%20heart%20ailments.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERisk%20factors%20include%20high%20blood%20pressure%2C%20high%20cholesterol%2C%20diabetes%2C%20smoking%2C%20and%20a%20family%20history%20of%20heart%20disease.%20If%20you%20have%20any%20of%20these%2C%20you%20should%20get%20regular%20check-ups.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CEvery%20adult%2C%20be%20it%20a%20woman%20or%20a%20man%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F288854%2Ftamil-nadu-auto-driver-daughter-tops-board-exams-after-fathers-heart-attack%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emust%20get%20yearly%20check-ups%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Check%20your%20blood%20pressure%20and%20sugar%2C%20especially%20if%20you%20have%20a%20family%20history%20of%20heart%20disease.%20If%20any%20of%20these%20levels%20are%20elevated%2C%20treat%20them%20on%20time.%20Heart%20diseases%20are%20preventable%20if%20these%20risk%20factors%20are%20in%20check%20and%20monitored%20regularly%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Dr%20Jaswal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdditional%20risk%20factors%20for%20women%20include%20pregnancy%20complications.%20If%20a%20woman%20has%20gestational%20diabetes%20or%20preeclampsia%20(high%20blood%20pressure)%2C%20the%20risk%20of%20heart%20disease%20later%20increases.%20Therefore%2C%20doctors%20stress%20that%20it%20is%20vital%20for%20women%20of%20all%20ages%20to%20prioritise%20their%20heart%20health.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20World%20Heart%20Federation%2C%20women%20also%20tend%20to%20have%20more%20severe%20first%20heart%20attacks%20that%20more%20frequently%20lead%20to%20death%20compared%20to%20men.%20%E2%80%9CWomen%20are%20the%20forefront%20and%20backbone%20of%20the%20family.%20Yet%2C%20they%20quietly%20die%20due%20to%20sudden%20cardiac%20arrests%2C%20and%20not%20much%20is%20spoken%20about%20it.%20It%E2%80%99s%20time%20that%20women%20recognise%20the%20warning%20signs%20and%20rush%20to%20the%20hospital%20any%20time%20they%20experience%20any%20of%20the%20symptoms%2C%E2%80%9D%20Dr%20Jaswal%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20also%20urges%20women%20to%20have%20yearly%20health%20check-ups%20and%20take%20immediate%20action%20if%20any%20of%20their%20levels%20are%20high.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENeha%E2%80%99s%20prompt%20thinking%20probably%20saved%20her%20life.%20You%20too%20can%20save%20yours%20by%20taking%20care%20of%20your%20health%20and%20acting%20promptly.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CTime%20is%20critical%20during%20a%20heart%20attack%2C%20and%20even%20a%20minute%20can%20turn%20the%20situation%20around%20for%20a%C2%A0%20person.%20In%20crucial%20times%2C%20you%20should%20trust%20your%20instincts%2C%20and%20if%20something%20feels%20wrong%2C%20you%20should%20immediately%20seek%20medical%20attention%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Dr%20Rao.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Arunava%20Banerjee%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1727419891000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fheart-care-1040227_1280-1727414916.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D367755%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Heart%20disease%20manifests%20differently%20in%20women%20and%20is%20an%20oft%20ignored%20subject.%20We%20spoke%20to%20doctors%20who%20explained%20the%20different%20symptoms%20women%20experience%20and%20the%20warning%20signs%20that%20must%20not%20be%20ignored.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Sowmya%20Mani%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F367755%2Fworld-heart-day-heart-disease-heart-attack-women-symptoms-warning-signs-cardiologists%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22How%20Kamal%20Malik%20Restored%20Asia%E2%80%99s%20Oldest%20Ice%20Factory%20%26amp%3B%20Turned%20it%20Into%20IF.BE%20in%20Mumbai%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EUnsure%20of%20what%20to%20do%20in%20Mumbai%20this%20weekend%3F%20Here%E2%80%99s%20an%20idea%3A%20Take%20a%20trip%20to%20the%20city%E2%80%99s%20south%2C%20the%20plush%20neighbourhood%20of%20Ballard%20Estate%20in%20particular.%20As%20you%20walk%20down%20Calicut%20Road%20%E2%80%93%20a%20street%20named%20after%20the%20traders%20from%20Calicut%20(present-day%20Kozhikode)%20who%20settled%20in%20the%20city%20%E2%80%93%20you%20are%20likely%20to%20see%20a%20two-storeyed%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F358205%2Ftiny-farm-fort-homestay-rishikesh-raghav-ansh-kumar-delhi-architects-cob-sustainable-home%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Earchitectural%20marvel%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20IF.BE.%20What%20began%20its%20journey%20as%20an%20ice%20factory%20in%201878%2C%20now%20serves%20as%20a%20space%20for%20creative%20minds%20to%20discuss%20art%20and%20ideas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20IF.BE%20isn%E2%80%99t%20hosting%20a%20stand-up%20show%20by%20comedian%20Masoom%20Rajwani%2C%20it%20finds%20itself%20overwhelmed%20by%20cinema%20aficionados.%20Yes%2C%20the%20scramble%20for%20a%20front-row%20seat%20to%20director%20Zoya%20Akhtar%E2%80%99s%20session%20on%20storytelling%20is%20real.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20these%20maestros%20aren%E2%80%99t%20gracing%20the%20dais%2C%20there%20are%20meditative%20movement%20workshops%2C%20film%20screenings%20and%20art%20exhibitions%20to%20sign%20up%20for.%20IF.BE%E2%80%99s%20social%20calendar%20lives%20up%20to%20its%20definition%20of%20a%20space%20where%20architects%2C%20designers%20and%20artists%20can%20converge%20and%20collaborate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fsustainable-architecture_11zon-1726746932.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Ambico%20Ice%20Factory%20is%20a%20145%20year%20old%20heritage%20building%20in%20South%20Bombay%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fsustainable-architecture_11zon-1726746932.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fsustainable-architecture_11zon-1726746932-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fsustainable-architecture_11zon-1726746932-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fsustainable-architecture_11zon-1726746932-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fsustainable-architecture_11zon-1726746932-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-366734%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20Ambico%20Ice%20Factory%20is%20a%20145-year-old%20heritage%20building%20in%20South%20Bombay%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHow%20did%20this%20transformation%20happen%3F%20An%20%E2%80%9Calmost%20poetic%E2%80%9D%20experience%20that%20Kamal%20Malik%20%E2%80%94%20an%20architect%20with%20almost%20five%20decades%20of%20experience%20%E2%80%94%20had%20when%20his%20eyes%20first%20met%20the%20almost%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F139833%2Fheritage-mumbai-temple-restored%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E150-year-old%20building%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMy%20first%20encounter%20with%20the%20Ice%20Factory%20is%20vividly%20etched%20in%20my%20memory!%20Sunlight%20streaming%20in%20from%20the%20north-light%20Burma%20teak%20trusses%20and%20piercing%20the%20blocks%20of%20ice%20being%20moved%20by%20the%20gantry%20and%20giving%20way%20to%20a%20courtyard%20shaded%20by%20the%20canopy%20of%20a%20huge%20banyan%20tree.%20A%20fertile%20environment%20for%20contemplation%20and%20transformation%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EAn%20ice%20factory%2C%20a%20banyan%20tree%2C%20and%20the%20birth%20of%20an%20idea%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20you%20set%20sight%20on%20IF.BE%20%E2%80%94%20an%20acronym%20for%20Ice%20Factory%20Bellary%20Estate%20%E2%80%94%20which%20also%20has%20a%20deeper%20meaning%20as%20Malik%20will%20explain%20later%2C%20you%20may%20find%20it%20hard%20to%20believe%20that%20what%20is%20now%20a%20creative%20hub%20for%20the%20arts%2C%20was%20an%20ice%20factory%20a%20century%20ago.%20So%20order%20yourself%20some%3Cem%3E%20matar%20khasta%20%3C%2Fem%3Erolls%20(fried%20finger%20food%20with%20green%20pea%20filling)%20while%20I%20regale%20you%20with%20a%20history%20lesson.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIF.BE%E2%80%99s%20walls%2C%20150%20years%20ago%2C%20would%20be%20privy%20to%20conversations%20of%20factory%20workers%20that%20ranged%20from%20whether%20the%20gantry%20was%20working%20properly%20to%20concerns%20about%20being%20able%20to%20meet%20the%20ice%20demand%20of%20fish%20markets%20in%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F72036%2Fmumbai-cafe-military-iconic-widely-loved-why%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESouth%20Bombay%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmbico%20Ice%20Factory%20(as%20it%20was%20known%20then)%20enjoyed%20its%20popularity%20for%20decades%20before%20a%20factory%20in%20New%20Bombay%20took%20over%20operations.%20%E2%80%9CIce%20first%20came%20to%20India%20on%20a%20ship%20from%20Boston%20in%20the%201800s%2C%E2%